title: Unlike Washington, Russia Makes Every Effort to Bring Peace to Middle East
text: Moscow's diplomatic and military efforts in Syria offer hope for the country and the whole Middle East which have been plagued by wars and destruction largely as a result of Washington's military engagement in the region, Die Freie Welt observed. ...
